

README for Tools
-----------------

Upper Layer: Java, TOSSIM, Motelab

. convertMotelab.pl: Parses motelab output
. convertTOSSIM.pl : Parses TOSSIM output

Lower level processing tools:

. processSkew.pl: Computes the clock skew and spits out in gnuplot format
. processEvents.pl: Looks at events, and spits out frequency range. Done 
                    for single hop context. 
                    Creates one file per node.

. doExperiments.pl: Runs experiments with different ignore periods.
. fitData.pl: Fits a line to the data (y= mx + c, computes m, c).
. fixEarlyData.pl: Fixed the earlier data.